# Optional. Only needed if the dashboard is served from a different
# host/port than the server (e.g. during dev: dashboard on :5173, server
# on :3000). If unset, the dashboard connects to whatever host/port it
# was itself loaded from — which is what happens automatically once the
# server serves the built dashboard directly (npm run build, then the
# server's static file serving takes over). See docs/SEAMLESS_DEPLOY.md.
# VITE_WS_URL=ws://localhost:3000
